com.whirvis.jraknet.protocol.login

Class ConnectionRequestAccepted

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.whirvis.jraknet.Packet
      • com.whirvis.jraknet.RakNetPacket
        • com.whirvis.jraknet.protocol.login.ConnectionRequestAccepted
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Failable

    public final class ConnectionRequestAccepted
extends RakNetPacket
implements Failable
    A CONNECTION_REQUEST_ACCEPTED packet.

    This packet is sent by the server during login after the CONNECTION_REQUEST packet to indicate that a client's connection has been accepted.

    Since:
    JRakNet v1.0.0
    Author:
    Whirvis T. Wheatley
